WHIMPY: Set automatic flee threshold (also: wimpy)

Syntax: whimpy <percent>
        whimpy off

DESCRIPTION:
  Sets an HP percentage below which your character will automatically
  attempt to flee from combat. When your current HP drops below this
  threshold, flee is triggered at the start of your next round.

  whimpy 30   : auto-flee when HP drops below 30%
  whimpy off  : disable auto-flee
  wimpy       : alternate spelling, works identically

NOTES:
  - Flee is not guaranteed to succeed.
  - Auto-flee consumes 1 APM.
  - Set to 0 or "off" to disable.

SEE ALSO: flee, wimpy, combat
